oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Guns N Roses at the Nissan Stadium
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (black, silver, and gold on white) announcing Guns N Roses at the Nissan Stadium on July 9. Poster features a metal photoplate and a woodcut of a skull, pistol and roses. Poster is a limited edition of 400.
